ptolemy.domains.de.lib.aspect

Class AFDXVlink

  • java.lang.Object
    • ptolemy.domains.de.lib.aspect.AFDXVlink

  • public class AFDXVlink
extends java.lang.Object
    This java object implements a virtual-link which belongs to the end-system of an AFDX Network. For more information please refer to: AFDX network simulation using PtolemyII.
    Since:
    Ptolemy II 10.0
    Version:
    $Id$
    Author:
    G. Lasnier
